# 📱 Saskatchewan Frontline Law App  

A mobile-first reference tool for **law enforcement officers in Saskatchewan, Canada**.  
Provides quick access to:  
- Provincial statutes & regulations  
- Criminal Code classifications  
- Penalties & charge wording  
- Lite Mode (Top 5 Acts) vs Full Mode (12 Acts)  

---

## 🚀 Install APK on Android
1. Go to your repo’s **GitHub → Actions → Latest workflow run**.  
2. Download artifact: `sk-law-app-apk.zip`.  
3. Extract → `app-debug.apk`.  
4. Copy to your phone & install.  

---

## 🛠️ Dev Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/clayniklas7725/sk-frontline-law.git
cd sk-frontline-law
npm install
npm run dev
